{
  "stem": "10181.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 62.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And probably canned-- you know, those-- you had some canned goods already, whatever they could get.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, Whatever was available, they would send, whatever they thought would be useful to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the people who actively did this and was in [INAUDIBLE] actually at the time, I didn't know was working for the underground.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was part of her-- her job, really, to-- to-- amongst other things, to-- to send supplies to people in prisons, you know, try to supply them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- she didn't do this directly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was done through various channels in order for the Germans not to be able to trace anybody because one way for the Germans to trace people was to find out who sent those parcels.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was done all in-- in-- you know, indirectly, but she was responsible for that most of the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And other people, too, got parcels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not the only ones, but we got a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember, it was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, it-- it was-- I remember that at one time I was embarrassed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, every day there was two of these parcels came in our name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, luckily, we were living in the orphanage, so we-- you know, it's-- Berenbaum decided from the beginning everything should be shared, which was right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was obviously the correct thing to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, well, do you want to keep a few candies for yourself?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I-- you know, let's-- let's everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was OK, but it was-- I remember this lady at the time came nearly every day to-- to-- to push parcels under the wire.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were the only ones who got that many.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then what happened when you came back out of the hospital?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was back in the orphanage, and the orphanage was more or less a life of-- that tried to be normal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had some sort of schooling there, teaching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of teachers in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a famous author-- children's author called Clara Asscher-Pinkhof, her name was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still can see her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In my mind, I can still see her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was very good with little kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't teach us, but she was very good with little kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Westerbork, also, at one time or another, there were very famous people there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, the Dutch Jews were very integrated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For instance, the orchestra, the concert orchestra, all the violinists, I think to the very last one, were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So at one time, they picked them all up and brought them to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then the Germans asked them to give a concert for them, you know, so they gave a concert for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they probably thought that if they gave concerts for the Germans, they would be deferred.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, they were deferred for maybe a week or two.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I think if I remember rightly reading afterwards the story of Westerbork, that I think one survived of the whole-- of this whole group of violinists.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then-- there was-- I don't remember his name-- there was a famous Jewish boxer who was well known, Dutch Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was bought into the camp, so he started organizing, like, exercising and-- and teaching young men if they want to box.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was to-- you know, so they used to have boxing exhibitions for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This-- this was a crazy situation when you think about it, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was a camp where-- where next week you might be dead, but the Germans came and watched you an exhibition of boxing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or they had a concert, or they had plays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, they-- they had plays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "People were performing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had people who were-- who were actors, and they performed and-- and-- and all these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Of course, they also performed for the inmates, you know, but the Germans had-- had them perform for them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And especially around Christmas time, you know, they could do that kind of thing, or any holiday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we, as I said, they tried to teach us to be good Jews in-- in the orphanage, and, of course, it was religious.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and-- and we had regular meal times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had to pray before and after the meal, and, like I said, to try to have sort of classes within the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then we used to walk around the camp, look for friends and visit friends, and-- and it was confined.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was-- it was thousands upon thousands of people in a very small area.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
